## Tests

Tests live next to their source as `*.test.ts`. The fastest way to
learn behavior for matching, policy, contract routing, milestones,
status responder, deadline monitor, activity, activity-timeline,
context, document assessment, validation, clock, and inbound
normalization is to read the corresponding `*.test.ts` first.

There is no end-to-end test for `intake.ts`; rely on the smaller unit
tests of the modules it composes.
